               <p>The Prosecutor depos'd, That he being a <rs id="t17270517-12-viclabel66" type="occupation">Watchman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17270517-12-victim93 t17270517-12-viclabel66"></join>, coming home before his usual Time, heard his wife cry out Murder before he came to the Door, and making what haste he could he got within Doors just as the Prisoner was secur'd.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17270517-12-person94">
                  Ann 
