             depos'd, That she bolted the Door at Night when she went to Bed, and that the Prisoner had by Violence wrenched off the Staple</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17270517-12-person95">
                  Elizabeth 
                  Shepherd 
               <interp inst="t17270517-12-person95" type="surname" value="Shepherd"></interp>
